<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[القاف والزاي]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(و. ا. ي)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">زوق:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">الزّاوُوْقُ:</span> الزِّئْبَقُ <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<span class="c5"> يُقال:</span> بَيْتٌ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> مُزَوَّقٌ أي مُزَيَّنٌ،<span class="c5"> وقيل:</span> مُقَوَّمٌ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[وزَوَّقَ كلامَه]</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">قوز:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">القَوْزُ من الرَّمْلِ:</span> صَغِيرٌ مُسْتَدِيرٌ تُشَبَّهُ <span class="c2">(٤)</span> به أرْدَافُ النِّسَاءِ، والجميع الأقْوازُ والقِيْزَانُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">والتَّقَوُّزُ:</span> عَدْوُ الوَعِلِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">وتَقَوَّزَ البَيْتُ من المَدَر:</span> أي <span class="c2">(٥)</span> تَهَوَّرَ وتَهَوّى.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">واقْتَازَهَا النَّمِرُ:</span> أي أكَلَها.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">وقَوَّزَ النَّبْتُ:</span> كَثُرَ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">زيق:</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">الزِّيْقُ:</span> زِيْقُ الجَيْبِ المَكْفُوْف.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) في ك: الزنبق.<br>(٢) في ك: نبت.<br>(٣) زيادة من ت.<br>(٤) في ت: يشبه.<br>(٥) في ت: البيت من المدارى.</p> </div>